            "content": "### 🎯 Step 1: User Profile & Targeting\n\nThe workflow begins by defining your search parameters. \n\nThe **Add a Resume** node acts as a configuration file, storing your bio, salary expectations, and the list of job boards to monitor."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
